itemDisplayName: Deploy a 15 node, 2 Node Types Windows Service Fabric Cluster
description: This template allows you to deploy 10 Node, 2 Node Types Service Fabric Cluster with one node type exclusively supporting Stateless workloads on  Standard_D2_V2 Size VMSS.
summary: This template takes a minimum amount of parameters and deploys a 15 Node, 2 Node types, Stateless Windows Service Fabric Cluster
